mber":38,"Text":"Liashabi alyameeni"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"Thullatun mina alawwaleena"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":40,"Text":"Wathullatun mina alakhireena"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":41,"Text":"Waashabu alshshimali ma ashabu alshshimali"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":42,"Text":"Fee samoomin wahameemin"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":43,"Text":"Wathillin min yahmoomin"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":44,"Text":"La baridin wala kareemin"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":45,"Text":"Innahum kanoo qabla thalika mutrafeena"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":46,"Text":"Wakanoo yusirroona AAala alhinthi alAAatheemi"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":47,"Text":"Wakanoo yaqooloona aitha mitna wakunna turaban waAAithaman ainna lamabAAoothoona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":48,"Text":"Awa abaona alawwaloona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":49,"Text":"Qul inna alawwaleena waalakhireena"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":50,"Text":"LamajmooAAoona ila meeqati yawmin maAAloomin"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":51,"Text":"Thumma innakum ayyuha alddalloona almukaththiboona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":52,"Text":"Laakiloona min shajarin min zaqqoomin"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":53,"Text":"Famalioona minha albutoona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":54,"Text":"Fashariboona AAalayhi mina alhameemi"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":55,"Text":"Fashariboona shurba alheemi"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":56,"Text":"Hatha nuzuluhum yawma alddeeni"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":57,"Text":"Nahnu khalaqnakum falawla tusaddiqoona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":58,"Text":"Afaraaytum ma tumnoona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":59,"Text":"Aantum takhluqoonahu am nahnu alkhaliqoona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":60,"Text":"Nahnu qaddarna baynakumu almawta wama nahnu bimasbooqeena"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":61,"Text":"AAala an nubaddila amthalakum wanunshiakum fee ma la taAAlamoona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":62,"Text":"Walaqad AAalimtumu alnnashata aloola falawla tathakkaroona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":63,"Text":"Afaraaytum ma tahruthoona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":64,"Text":"Aantum tazraAAoonahu am nahnu alzzariAAoona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":65,"Text":"Law nashao lajaAAalnahu hutaman fathaltum tafakkahoona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":66,"Text":"Inna lamughramoona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":67,"Text":"Bal nahnu mahroomoona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":68,"Text":"Afaraaytumu almaa allathee tashraboona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":69,"Text":"Aantum anzaltumoohu mina almuzni am nahnu almunziloona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":70,"Text":"Law nashao jaAAalnahu ojajan falawla tashkuroona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":71,"Text":"Afaraaytumu alnnara allatee tooroona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":72,"Text":"Aantum anshatum shajarataha am nahnu almunshioona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":73,"Text":"Nahnu jaAAalnaha tathkiratan wamataAAan lilmuqweena"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":74,"Text":"Fasabbih biismi rabbika alAAatheemi"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":75,"Text":"Fala oqsimu bimawaqiAAi alnnujoomi"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":76,"Text":"Wainnahu laqasamun law taAAlamoona AAatheemun"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":77,"Text":"Innahu laquranun kareemun"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":78,"Text":"Fee kitabin maknoonin"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":79,"Text":"La yamassuhu illa almutahharoona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":80,"Text":"Tanzeelun min rabbi alAAalameena"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":81,"Text":"Afabihatha alhadeethi antum mudhinoona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":82,"Text":"WatajAAaloona rizqakum annakum tukaththiboona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":83,"Text":"Falawla itha balaghati alhulqooma"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":84,"Text":"Waantum heenaithin tanthuroona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":85,"Text":"Wanahnu aqrabu ilayhi minkum walakin la tubsiroona"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":86,"Text":"Falawla in kuntum ghayra madeeneena"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":87,"Text":"TarjiAAoonaha in kuntum sadiqeena"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":88,"Text":"Faamma in kana mina almuqarrabeena"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":89,"Text":"Farawhun warayhanun wajannatu naAAeemin"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":90,"Text":"Waamma in kana min ashabi alyameeni"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":91,"Text":"Fasalamun laka min ashabi alyameeni"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":92,"Text":"Waamma in kana mina almukaththibeena alddalleena"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":93,"Text":"Fanuzulun min hameemin"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":94,"Text":"Watasliyatu jaheemin"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":95,"Text":"Inna hatha lahuwa haqqu alyaqeeni"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":96,"Text":"Fasabbih biismi rabbika alAAatheemi"}]},{"LanguageCode":"eng","Language":"English","Name":"eng-mustafakhattabg","Author":"Mustafa Khattab God Edition","Source":"","Direction":"ltr","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"When the Inevitable Event takes place"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"then no one can deny it has come"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"It will debase ˹some˺ and elevate ˹others˺"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"When the earth will be violently shaken"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"and the mountains will be crushed to pieces"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"becoming scattered ˹particles of˺ dust"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"you will ˹all˺ be ˹divided into˺ three groups"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"the people of the right, how ˹blessed˺ will they be"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"the people of the left, how ˹miserable˺ will they be"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"and the foremost ˹in faith˺ will be the foremost ˹in Paradise˺"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"They are the ones nearest ˹to God˺"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"in the Gardens of Bliss"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"˹They will be˺ a multitude from earlier generations"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"and a few from later generations"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"˹All will be˺ on jewelled thrones"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"reclining face to face"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"They will be waited on by eternal youths"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"with cups, pitchers, and a drink ˹of pure wine˺ from a flowing stream"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"that will cause them neither headache nor intoxication"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"˹They will also be served˺ any fruit they choose"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"and meat from any bird they desire"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"And ˹they will have˺ maidens with gorgeous eyes"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"like pristine pearls"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":24,"Text":"˹all˺ as a reward for what they used to do"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":25,"Text":"There they will never hear any idle or sinful talk—"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":26,"Text":"only good and virtuous speech"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":27,"Text":"And the people of the right—how ˹blessed˺ will they be"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":28,"Text":"˹They will be˺ amid thornless lote trees"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":29,"Text":"clusters of bananas"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":30,"Text":"extended shade"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":31,"Text":"flowing water"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":32,"Text":"abundant fruit—"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":33,"Text":"never out of season nor forbidden—"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":34,"Text":"and elevated furnishings"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":35,"Text":"Indeed, We will have perfectly created their mates"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":36,"Text":"making them virgins"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":37,"Text":"loving and of equal age"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":38,"Text":"for the people of the right"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":39,"Text":"˹who will be˺ a multitude from earlier generations"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":40,"Text":"and a multitude from later generations"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":41,"Text":"And the people of the left—how ˹miserable˺ will they be"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":42,"Text":"˹They will be˺ in scorching heat and boiling water"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":43,"Text":"in the shade of black smoke"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":44,"Text":"neither cool nor refreshing"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":45,"Text":"Indeed, before this ˹torment˺ they were spoiled by luxury"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":46,"Text":"and persisted in the worst of sin"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":47,"Text":"They used to ask ˹mockingly˺, “When we are dead and reduced to dust and bones, will we really be resurrected"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":48,"Text":"And our forefathers as well?”"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":49,"Text":"Say, ˹O Prophet,˺ “Most certainly, earlier and later generations"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":50,"Text":"will surely be gathered ˹together˺ for the appointed Day"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":51,"Text":"Then you, O misguided deniers"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":52,"Text":"will certainly eat from ˹the fruit of˺ the trees of Zaqqûm"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":53,"Text":"filling up ˹your˺ bellies with it"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":54,"Text":"Then on top of that you will drink boiling water—"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":55,"Text":"and you will drink ˹it˺ like thirsty camels do.”"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":56,"Text":"This will be their accommodation on the Day of Judgment"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":57,"Text":"It is We Who created you. Will you not then believe ˹in resurrection˺"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":58,"Text":"Have you considered what you ejaculate"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":59,"Text":"Is it you who create ˹a child out of˺ it, or is it We Who do so"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":60,"Text":"We have ordained death for ˹all of˺ you, and We cannot be prevented"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":61,"Text":"from transforming and recreating you in forms unknown to you"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":62,"Text":"You already know how you were first created. Will you not then be mindful"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":63,"Text":"Have you considered what you sow"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":64,"Text":"Is it you who cause it to grow, or is it We Who do so"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":65,"Text":"If We willed, We could simply reduce this ˹harvest˺ to chaff, leaving you to lament"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":66,"Text":"“We have truly suffered a ˹great˺ loss"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":67,"Text":"In fact, we have been deprived ˹of our livelihood˺.”"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":68,"Text":"Have you considered the water you drink"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":69,"Text":"Is it you who bring it down from the clouds, or is it We Who do so"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":70,"Text":"If We willed, We could make it salty. Will you not then give thanks"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":71,"Text":"Have you considered the fire you kindle"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":72,"Text":"Is it you who produce its trees, or is it We Who do so"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":73,"Text":"We have made it ˹as˺ a reminder ˹of the Hellfire˺ and a provision for the travellers"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":74,"Text":"So glorify the Name of your Lord, the Greatest"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":75,"Text":"So I do swear by the positions of the stars—"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":76,"Text":"and this, if only you knew, is indeed a great oath—"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":77,"Text":"that this is truly a noble Quran"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":78,"Text":"in a well-preserved Record"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":79,"Text":"touched by none except the purified ˹angels˺"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":80,"Text":"˹It is˺ a revelation from the Lord of all worlds"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":81,"Text":"How can you then take this message lightly"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":82,"Text":"and repay ˹God for˺ your provisions with denial"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":83,"Text":"Why then ˹are you helpless˺ when the soul ˹of a dying person˺ reaches ˹their˺ throat"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":84,"Text":"while you are looking on"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":85,"Text":"And We are nearer to such a person than you, but you cannot see"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":86,"Text":"Now, if you are not subject to Our Will ˹as you claim˺"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":87,"Text":"bring that soul back, if what you say is true"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":88,"Text":"So, if the deceased is one of those brought near ˹to Us˺"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":89,"Text":"then ˹such a person will have˺ serenity, fragrance, and a Garden of Bliss"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":90,"Text":"And if the deceased is one of the people of the right"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":91,"Text":"then ˹they will be told,˺ “Greetings to you from the people of the right.”"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":92,"Text":"But if such person is one of the misguided deniers"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":93,"Text":"then their accommodation will be boiling water ˹to drink˺"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":94,"Text":"and burning in Hellfire"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":95,"Text":"Indeed, this is the absolute truth"},{"SurahNumber":56,"VerseNumber":96,"Text":"So glorify the Name of your Lord, the Greatest"}]}]}